name: What Dutch People Eat - Episode 2
description:
Time to eat Dutch and upset some Ducthies in the process :)

After I posted episode 1 of What Dutch People Eat I received lots and lots of suggestions of other Dutch food I should try.   So I just had to go back to Holland - sorry The Netherlands - to continue my food quest and each as much Dutch food as I could. 

This episode of What Dutch People Eat includes stampot, ewrten soup, pancakes, herring, rollmops, vla, more breakfast food, cheese, Dutch beer, uitsmijters and the famous frikandel.

Keep the suggestions coming and don't forget to subscribe. 

for more videos also check out my work channel with features lots of great destination videos from around the world - Bunnik Tours

Click here to see the videos: https://www.youtube.com/user/BunnikTours 

Enjoy!
